{"title":"Guía de mudanza de Seattle a Austin: Reubicación Completa [2026]","description":"Compara el costo de vida, vivienda, impuestos y calidad de vida al mudarte de Seattle a Austin. Guía de reubicación basada en datos con calculadoras.","url":"https://urcity.com/es/compare/gu%C3%ADa-de-mudanza-de-seattle-a-austin-reubicaci%C3%B3n-completa-2026/","content":"\u003ch2 id=\"introduction\"\u003eIntroduction\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSeattle and Austin are two of America\u0026rsquo;s top tech hubs — but Austin offers dramatically lower costs while maintaining a robust tech scene. If you\u0026rsquo;re tired of Seattle\u0026rsquo;s housing prices and rainy winters, Austin might be your answer.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"cost-of-living-comparison\"\u003eCost of Living Comparison\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003ctable\u003e\n\t\u003cthead\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eCategory\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eSeattle\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eAustin\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cth\u003eSavings\u003c/th\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\u003c/thead\u003e\n\t\u003ctbody\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eOverall Index\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e172.1\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e119.3\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e-31%\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eRent (1BR)\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$2,350/mo\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$1,650/mo\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e-$700/mo\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eHome Price\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$820,000\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$450,000\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e-45%\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eUtilities\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$130/mo\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$140/mo\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e+8%\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eGroceries\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$520/mo\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$380/mo\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e-27%\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eTransportation\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$170/mo\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$150/mo\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e-12%\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003ctr\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003eHealthcare\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$400/mo\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e$350/mo\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ctd\u003e-13%\u003c/td\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/tr\u003e\n\t\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMonthly savings potential: $1,200–$2,000\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"salary-calculator\"\u003eSalary Calculator\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you make \u003cstrong\u003e$120,000 in Seattle\u003c/strong\u003e, you need approximately \u003cstrong\u003e$83,000 in Austin\u003c/strong\u003e to maintain the same standard of living.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"calculator-widget\" id=\"salary-calc\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-header\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-icon amber\"\u003e\n      \u003csvg width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\n        \u003crect x=\"2\" y=\"7\" width=\"20\" height=\"14\" rx=\"2\"/\u003e\n        \u003cpath d=\"M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16\"/\u003e\n      \u003c/svg\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-title-group\"\u003e\n      \u003ch3\u003eCalculadora de Equivalencia Salarial\u003c/h3\u003e\n      \u003cp class=\"calc-subtitle\"\u003eDescubre cuánto necesitas ganar para mantener tu estilo de vida\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-inputs-row three-col\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n      \u003clabel for=\"current-salary\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cline x1=\"12\" y1=\"1\" x2=\"12\" y2=\"23\"/\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n        Salario Actual\n      \u003c/label\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"input-prefix\"\u003e\n        \u003cspan class=\"prefix\" id=\"salary-prefix\"\u003e$\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cinput type=\"number\" id=\"current-salary\" value=\"120000\" min=\"0\" step=\"1000\"\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n      \u003clabel for=\"from-city-input\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z\"/\u003e\u003ccircle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n        Ciudad de Origen\n      \u003c/label\u003e\n      \n\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"city-combobox\"\u003e\n  \u003cinput type=\"text\" id=\"from-city-input\" class=\"city-combobox-input\" placeholder=\"Buscar ciudades...\" autocomplete=\"off\" value=\"seattle-wa\"\u003e\n  \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"from-city\" value=\"seattle-wa\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"city-combobox-dropdown\" id=\"from-city-dropdown\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv class=\"calc-field\"\u003e\n      \u003clabel for=\"to-city-input\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z\"/\u003e\u003ccircle cx=\"12\" cy=\"10\" r=\"3\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n        Ciudad de Destino\n      \u003c/label\u003e\n      \n\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"city-combobox\"\u003e\n  \u003cinput type=\"text\" id=\"to-city-input\" class=\"city-combobox-input\" placeholder=\"Buscar ciudades...\" autocomplete=\"off\" value=\"austin-tx\"\u003e\n  \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" id=\"to-city\" value=\"austin-tx\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"city-combobox-dropdown\" id=\"to-city-dropdown\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003cbutton class=\"btn btn-primary btn-large\" onclick=\"calculateSalary()\"\u003e\n    \u003csvg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\u003cpolyline points=\"22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n    Calcular Salario Equivalente\n  \u003c/button\u003e\n\n  \u003cdiv class=\"calc-result\" id=\"salary-result\" style=\"display:none;\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv class=\"result-header\"\u003e\n      \u003ch4\u003eSalario Equivalente\u003c/h4\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"result-badge badge-neutral\" id=\"salary-badge\"\u003eResultado\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv class=\"salary-cards\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"salary-card from\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"salary-card-label\"\u003eActual\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"salary-card-city\" id=\"from-city-display\"\u003eCiudad A\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"salary-card-amount\" id=\"from-salary-display\"\u003e$100,000\u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv class=\"salary-arrow\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg width=\"32\" height=\"32\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"\u003e\n          \u003cline x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/\u003e\n          \u003cpolyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"/\u003e\n        \u003c/svg\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"salary-arrow-label\" id=\"salary-change-pct\"\u003e0%\u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv class=\"salary-card to\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"salary-card-label\"\u003eNecesitas\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"salary-card-city\" id=\"to-city-display\"\u003eCiudad B\u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"salary-card-amount\" id=\"needed-salary\"\u003e$100,000\u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv class=\"result-summary\" id=\"salary-difference\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cscript\u003e\nvar SALARY_CITIES = [\n\n\n\n{value:\"acapulco-gro\",col: 70.5 ,name:\"Acapulco\",display:\"Acapulco, México\",country:\"MX\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"adelaide-sa\",col: 82 ,name:\"Adelaide\",display:\"Adelaide, Australia\",country:\"AU\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"agrinio-wg\",col: 78 ,name:\"Agrinio\",display:\"Agrinio, Grecia\",country:\"GR\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"aguascalientes-agu\",col: 67.5 ,name:\"Aguascalientes\",display:\"Aguascalientes, México\",country:\"MX\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"akron-oh\",col: 88.5 ,name:\"Akron\",display:\"Akron, OH, US\",country:\"US\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"albuquerque-nm\",col: 94.5 ,name:\"Albuquerque\",display:\"Albuquerque, NM, US\",country:\"US\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"albury-nsw\",col: 65 ,name:\"Albury\",display:\"Albury, Australia\",country:\"AU\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"alexandroupoli-em\",col: 84 ,name:\"Alexandroupoli\",display:\"Alexandroupoli, Grecia\",country:\"GR\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"amsterdam-nl\",col: 82.1 ,name:\"Amsterdam\",display:\"Amsterdam, Países Bajos\",country:\"NL\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"anaheim-ca\",col: 148.5 ,name:\"Anaheim\",display:\"Anaheim, CA, US\",country:\"US\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"anchorage-ak\",col: 118.5 ,name:\"Anchorage\",display:\"Anchorage, AK, US\",country:\"US\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"ann-arbor-mi\",col: 108.5 ,name:\"Ann Arbor\",display:\"Ann Arbor, MI, US\",country:\"US\"},\n\n\n\n{value:\"ashevi